snippet.title: Star Fleet I : The War Begins Pt. 1(Commodore 64)
snippet.description: This is part 1 of a mostly complete playthrough of a short game of Star Fleet I : The War Begins on the Commodore 64. It had a little problem at the end due to using a fast loader (dont use a fast loader for this game) so the end of the mission doesn't play through but its mostly there *With Sound* if your interested I can put up a video without sound that does show the end. This is my third attempt now to get sound on these things. Lets see if it works this time.
